{
  "stem": "19921.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And again, we started out again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we continued.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We continued for 12 days until we got to a large city by the name of Lwow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we stopped there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That was a large city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The front line was still away from Lwow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The Germans were not close there, and we stopped there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Now, Lwow was not far away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "As far as I remember, it could have been about 100 kilometer away from the-- from the Russian border.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was the farthest town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Let me continue on that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So we stopped in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Then, a couple days later, the Germans and the Russians entered a agreement, a pact.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Russia declared-- the Soviet Union attacked and declared war on Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, it didn't take them long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They occupied city of Lwow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they annexed that territory there, and we get-- I got stuck together with my-- rest of the-- of my family in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were living in Lwow for one week when the Russian army all of a sudden came in and annexed that-- the-- they proceeded to continue, you know, more east.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were stuck in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Didn't know anything what will develop at that particular time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were living in Lwow till May of 1940.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now how did you live then?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How did you support yourself under the Russians there?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Under the Russians there, we'd strictly support ourselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever we had, we sold and-- to buy bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were able to find some little things to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not much, not much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Little things.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One of my uncles were able to find a job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Two of my uncles, actually, were able to find a job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we just were pitching in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We still had, you know, money here and there.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
